issue.title: Fix KMeans segfault

repository.name: DeepLabCut
repository.description: Official implementation of DeepLabCut: Markerless pose estimation of user-defined features with deep learning for all animals incl. humans

license.name: GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0

issue.body:
scikit-image was the culprit; adding that line alone (`from skimage.util import img_as_ubyte`) was enough to make sklearn MiniBatchKMeans crash with v0.18.2 and v0.18.3...so enforcing <=0.18.1 for now

Fixes #1522

body:
@lilstarhunter @davidmurray we found the culprit, scikit-image ... so please this in your conda env, and you'll be all set :D 
```
pip install --upgrade git+https://github.com/deeplabcut/deeplabcut.git
```
@MMathisLab Right on! Works now. Thank you so much!
